The paper deals with computer vision tasks, specifically American Sign Language recognition, which suggests that it falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses advancements in deep model architectures and model parameter initialization, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of generative multi-stream architecture and spatio-temporal residual block also suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of computer graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with language recognition, which could also place it under the natural language processing (cs.CL) category.
